            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chicken is cooking, heat a pot with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>chopped cherry tomatoes</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until beginning to break down</p><p>Add the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and cook for 30 secs, then add 100ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[130ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[150ml]</span> <strong>water</strong> with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong> and cook for 4-5 min further or until thickened – this is your <strong>tomato sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-6-1600417756205-x200.jpg",
