    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>breaded chicken </strong>over the <strong>tomato & basil sauce </strong>with the <strong>crispy potatoes</strong> and<strong> shredded lettuce</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle the <strong>mustard dressing </strong>over the shredded lettuce</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
